---
title: Herby Chicken & Parmesan-Cauli Mash with Veggies & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Pair chicken breast with our homely garlic and herb seasoning and you’ve got a match made in heaven. With a
creamy low-carb mash and dill-parsley mayo wanting to join in on the fun, we just couldn’t say no. More is more in
our books, and you’ll love us for it!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
